  "texts": [
    "This tutor bot was built using ChatGPT 3.5 as this version is a publicly available system in the university in which students have access to and can use.",
    "We do note that at the current time of writing, LLM technologies have been vastly improved with more powerful versions such as GPT-4o.",
    "The tutor bot was designed to actively engage students and assist them in comprehending concepts through explanations and interactive questioning.",
    "The tutor's specific topic of discussion was educational reform within a global context.",
    "Participants were asked to provide information about their level of learning, to present an example of an educational reform, to respond to relevant questions about the reforms, and to write summaries (Table 1)."
  ],
